---
layout: base
permalink: /index.html
title: 'Neural Flow'
description: "The Website of Daniel Scott-Raynsford: An AI adventurer and builder."
blog:
  title: 'Blog'
  intro: "My recent blog posts."
---

<div class="wrapper">
  <header class="full | section" style="--spot-color: var(--color-primary)">
    <div class="section__inner flow region">
      <h1 class="text-center" style="color: var(--color-light);">{{ title }}</h1>
    </div>
    {% svg "divider/waves", null, "divider" %}
  </header>

  <article class="full | region">
    <div class="wrapper flow prose">
      <h2 id="an-eleventy-starter">Neural Flow</h2>
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Daniel, I'm a software engineer and AI enthusiast.
      </p>
      <p>
        Welcome to my website, where I share my journey into building intelligent systems with AI.
        I share my thoughts, ideas, and projects related to AI, software development and building intelligent systems in the cloud.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <section class="full | region">
    <div class="wrapper flow prose">
      <h2>{{ blog.title }}</h2>
      {% if blog.intro %}
        <p>{{ blog.intro }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="feature |  region region-space-l">
        <custom-masonry layout="50-50">
          {% set itemList = collections.allPosts %}
					{% asyncEach item in itemList.slice(0, 4) %}
            {% set headingLevel = "h3" %}
						{% include "partials/card-blog.njk" %}
					{% endeach %}
        </custom-masonry>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
